entries.femaleVariant: Hey, V! Jefferson Peralez here. You know, mayor of Night City.
I'm callin' about our recent program to tackle homelessness.
What would you say about bein' the head of my security detail, huh?
As you know, the number of people I can trust are few and far between. Next week we're gonna be raisin' the city's taxes, so things might get a little hairy.
Come by and we'll hammer out a good deal for you... I'm no ennypincher when it comes to safety.
All right, well, we'll be in touch, V.
V, you're gonna wanna hear this, but first you need to go somewhere no one's listenin'.
OK, so my wife, Elizabeth... she's in on the whole thing.
She-she keeps saying I should look after myself... tells me to take these pills... says they're vitamins.
Got 'em analyzed at a lab a-and they look OK, b-but how am I supposed to know if somebody didn't falsify the results?
W-w-when you've got a sec, call me, OK? Oh yeah, and don't forget to delete this message.
